      <div class="o-grid__item u-1/1 u-2/3@md" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150">
      </div>
      <div class="o-grid__item u-1/1 u-1/3@md" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="c-section">
  <div class="o-container">
    <div class="o-grid o-grid--padded">

      <div class="o-grid__item u-1/1 u-1/3@md">
        <p class="label">Lorem ipsum dolor amet</p>
        <p>Cras mattis consectetur purus sit amet fermentum. Donec ullamcorper nulla non metus auctor fringilla. Aenean eu leo quam. Pellentesque ornare sem lacinia quam venenatis vestibulum. Donec ullamcorper nulla non metus auctor fringilla. Curabitur blandit tempus porttitor. Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut id elit. Aenean lacinia bibendum nulla sed consectetur.

